{"tid":1364634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美屬波多黎各連日示威 總督終屈服下台","createTime":"2019-07-25T11:48:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T22:11:27.000Z","uid":113000,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cf1e4acd342d85a7177557d524984f9809e3416d","tid":1364634,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:48:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2410763\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2410763&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6YCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=2b6ffe4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2410763</a><br />\n<br />\n位於加勒比海的美屬波多黎各（Puerto Rico）大批民眾連續逾一星期上街，要求曾發表恐同、仇女言論的總督羅塞略（Ricardo Rossell&oacute;）下台。曾表明拒絕下台的羅塞略終於屈服，宣布會在8月2日下台。<br />\n<br />\n法務部長巴斯克斯（Wanda Vazquez）料會接任波多黎各總督一職。<br />\n<br />\n羅塞略早前被揭發，與多名官員的聊天群組內發表恐同、仇女言論，更曾拿颶風瑪莉亞（Hurricane Maria）的受害者開玩笑。<br />\n<br />\n數以千計的示威者連日來堵塞一條首都的主要公路，周一更有百萬人上街，為波多黎各近20年來最大型示威。<br />\n<br />\n美屬波多黎各百萬人上街 失職總督拒下台 僅承諾不尋求連任<br />\n<br />\n當地民眾表示，羅塞略的辭職只是波多黎各政權，出現歷史性改變的第一步。不少民眾對兩大政黨，新進步黨（New Progressive Party）及人民民主黨（Popular Democratic Party）都失去信心。<br />\n<br />\n波多黎各大學心理學家科林指（Cynthia Garc&iacute;a Coll）形容，羅塞略僅是一個深層問題的一項症狀。科林指，波多黎各人以往只會看着電視抱怨，但甚麼都不做，現時人們不再只坐在電視機前了，這就是和平革命。"},{"pid":"ad076a66aeea9605565f9c362fa1dfd20b6a1d3b","tid":1364634,"uid":113000,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:50:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />投胎首抽真係好重要<br />\n<br />\n十日就攪掂"},{"pid":"811294890856d6681a9c056b66c04a10a87e5471","tid":1364634,"uid":113000,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:52:07.000Z","msg":"數以千計的示威者連日來堵塞一條首都的主要公路，周一更有百萬人上街，為波多黎各近20年來最大型示威。<br />\n<br />\n相映成趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca582f656749b5663564f878e3260e8b6324299","tid":1364634,"uid":30040,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:56:06.000Z","msg":"民主國家同唔係民主國家既分別"},{"pid":"8c25549002ad0dc4a90c204de9847dea04611a1a","tid":1364634,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:08:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d83d05871f87ee6d691b3625db2badf2dbc6f28e","tid":1364634,"uid":273753,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:11:14.000Z","msg":"兩次開埠以來最大型的示威都無反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc78e9a4fa72b455a2375419f16d12c7edfb4e72","tid":1364634,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:12:17.000Z","msg":"先有蘇丹後有波多黎各<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecb36dca7b86b6eec90f81c2505306d0afc36e8d","tid":1364634,"uid":4346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:13:14.000Z","msg":"美屬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a839e6d2a93b809bfcba69a0436a2cae50c2b4","tid":1364634,"uid":209248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:13:23.000Z","msg":"有民主同無民主分別"},{"pid":"a5c1f552e00946b09d5bc763460936ff55994de3","tid":1364634,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:04:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b86049e79c394ff0371748fd1d58732cba39eba","tid":1364634,"uid":256309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:16:52.000Z","msg":"相比林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a195bb96bab4672aae03a57c181d112bd2eac0","tid":1364634,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T22:11:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}